Quartet of Crickets 2024-02-03 8:21 PM
The way I separate my tics, compulsions, and stims is Tics- something that happens pretty much automatically and can't really be helped Compulsions- something that could in theory be helped, but it's a lot easier said than done. While I can technically control them, I feel like I have to do them or something just isn't right, and it's hard to stop them once you start them. Stims- Just something nice to do to help relax that generally isn't frustrating or harmful There is some overlap sometimes though
